name: py-kt-legacy

variants.name: build_system
variants.description: Build systems supported by the package

description:
This repository is to support the deprecated import name of Keras Tuner.
With this repo, you can import Keras Tuner as kerastuner. In the main
Keras Tuner repository the import name has been changed to keras_tuner.
